ss=\\\"atn\\\">type<\\/span><span class=\\\"pun\\\">=<\\/span><span class=\\\"atv\\\">\\\"submit\\\"<\\/span><span class=\\\"tag\\\">&gt;<\\/span><span class=\\\"pln\\\">Button<\\/span><span class=\\\"tag\\\">&lt;\\/button&gt;<\\/span><\\/li><li class=\\\"L2\\\"><span class=\\\"tag\\\">&lt;input<\\/span><span class=\\\"pln\\\"> <\\/span><span class=\\\"atn\\\">class<\\/span><span class=\\\"pun\\\">=<\\/span><span class=\\\"atv\\\">\\\"btn\\\"<\\/span><span class=\\\"pln\\\"> <\\/span><span class=\\\"atn\\\">type<\\/span><span class=\\\"pun\\\">=<\\/span><span class=\\\"atv\\\">\\\"button\\\"<\\/span><span class=\\\"pln\\\"> <\\/span><span class=\\\"atn\\\">value<\\/span><span class=\\\"pun\\\">=<\\/span><span class=\\\"atv\\\">\\\"Input\\\"<\\/span><span class=\\\"tag\\\">&gt;<\\/span><\\/li><li class=\\\"L3\\\"><span class=\\\"tag\\\">&lt;input<\\/span><span class=\\\"pln\\\"> <\\/span><span class=\\\"atn\\\">class<\\/span><span class=\\\"pun\\\">=<\\/span><span class=\\\"atv\\\">\\\"btn\\\"<\\/span><span class=\\\"pln\\\"> <\\/span><span class=\\\"atn\\\">type<\\/span><span class=\\\"pun\\\">=<\\/span><span class=\\\"atv\\\">\\\"submit\\\"<\\/span><span class=\\\"pln\\\"> <\\/span><span class=\\\"atn\\\">value<\\/span><span class=\\\"pun\\\">=<\\/span><span class=\\\"atv\\\">\\\"Submit\\\"<\\/span><span class=\\\"tag\\\">&gt;<\\/span><\\/li><\\/ol><\\/pre><br>\\r\\n  <p>As a best practice, try to match the element for your context to ensure matching cross-browser rendering. If you have an <code>input<\\/code>, use an <code>&lt;input type=\\\"submit\\\"&gt;<\\/code> for your button.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2016-05-23 02:07:35\",\"created_by\":\"824\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2017-12-15 11:28:43\",\"modified_by\":\"824\",\"checked_out\":\"824\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2017-12-15 11:28:02\",\"publish_up\":\"2016-05-23 02:07:35\",\"publish_down\":\